                  </hi>, Esq. (<hi rend="italic">solicitor</hi>). The prosecutors names are William James Chaplin and Benjamin Worthy Home.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I did not say what the policeman says—I was lying where he states, but. was not near the cart.</p>
